		<p>Basically an app that turns your phone into a dashcam. A dash cam is a type of security camera that records video on an n-minute loop, and if an accident or other event occurs (maybe if accelerometer values go through the roof), you can save the most recently captured video permanently. Look up "Russian dashcam footage" for examples. This could be integrated with the second project. <br />
		Hardware needed: See above.</p>
	</div>

